SubjectOrder Approving that National Capital Commission Extend the lease with Turnstone Biologics Inc.
PrecisOrder approving that National Capital Commission grant an option to extend the lease with TURNSTONE BIOLOGICS INC. for a period of five years, beginning on December 1, 2024, for the real property located at 12-18 York Street, Suite 300, in Ottawa, Ontario.
